    "It allows for the creation of tailored learning scenarios that can adapt to the needs and abilities of individual students, making learning more engaging and effective (Eager & Brunton, 2023).",
    "One of the most significant impacts of prompt engineering is its potential to enhance learning experiences and foster critical thinking.",
    "By carefully designing prompts, educators can encourage students to approach problems from different perspectives, analyze information critically, and develop solutions creatively.",
    "This approach not only deepens their understanding of the subject matter but also hones their critical thinking skills, an essential competency in today's fastpaced and ever-changing world.",
    "As one particular study showed, learning to prompt effectively in the classroom can even help students realize more about the limits of AI, which inevitably fosters their AI literacy (Theophilou et al., 2023)."
